<div id="zh-question-title" data-editable="false">

<h2 class="zm-item-title zm-editable-content">

<a href="/question/20696837">怎样克服「选择恐惧症」？</a>

</h2>
</div>
<div id="zh-question-detail" class="zm-item-rich-text" data-resourceid="459225" data-action="/question/detail">

<div class="zm-editable-content">大事儿面前有犹豫很正常；<br>有人对于两件同款衬衫具体该选哪个颜色、晚饭到底吃哪家这类小事儿面前也会迟疑，磨磨蹭蹭选了半天 还是会后悔怎么没选另一个！</div>


</div>
