<li itemprop="itemListElement" itemscope itemtype="http://schema.org/Question"><a class="question_link" href="/question/19683263">如何克服社交恐惧症？</a> <span class="num">85 个回答</span><meta itemprop="followerCount" content="3614" /></li>

